What you need to know:

Mr Ruto insisted that he had executed his duties as per the Constitution.He has been having frosty relations with the President to a point where Dr Ruto skips high-level meetings hosted by his boss.MP Kanini Kega threatened to cut funding to the DP’s office for what he said was dereliction of duty.Wednesday, Mr Ichung’wah dared Mr Kega, the Kieni MP, to go ahead with his plan.